abstract: Simona Halep beats Timea Babos in second round of Guangzhou International Womens Open; other tennis results noted.
lead_paragraph: Top-seeded Simona Halep defeated Timea Babos, 6-4, 6-0, in second-round play in the Guangzhou International Women’s Open in China.

headline.main: Halep and Errani Advance to Third Round in China
